'''Gamers2''' is a Spanish organization, which was officially launched on February 24, 2014.

The team participated in the [[Riot_League_Championship_Series/Europe/2015_Season/Spring_Expansion|Spring Expansion Tournament]], beating [[Reason Gaming]] in the seeding game and [[Team Strix]] in Round 1. Gamers2 were knocked out of the tournament in Round 2 after being beaten by [[n!faculty]].
